
// This Hyperlambda code snippet changes the value of the [type] node to the value retrieved from the [type] node inside the [.arguments] node. It uses the [set-value] slot to modify the [type] node and the [get-value] slot to fetch the value from the specified node. The code effectively updates the [type] node with the value of the [type] argument provided in the [.arguments] node.
set-value:x:@.type
